The paper deals with the problem of subgraph matching on large-scale graphs, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of graph indices is also mentioned, which is a topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and search engines (cs.SI). Finally, the use of parallel computing is discussed, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC).
